---
import Layout from "../layouts/defaultLayout.astro";
import ChatButton from "../components/chatButton.astro";
import MusicProfile from "../components/musicProfile.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";

const artists = [
  { name: "Obongjayar", image: "/artists/bigob.webp"},
  { name: "Jacob Banks", image: "artists/jacobbanks.webp"},
  { name: "Tems", image: "/artists/tems.webp"},
  { name: "BLK ODYSSY", image: "/artists/blkodyssy.webp"},
  { name: "Masego", image: "/artists/masego.webp"},
]
---

<Layout>
  <main class="pt-28 pb-32">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-9">
      <div class="lg:col-span-4">
        <div class="font-bold mb-8">At the moment, I'm ..</div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-7 gap-8">
          <div class="activity-card bg-[#2EC94F] sm:col-span-3">
            <div class="relative p-4">
              <div class="lowercase !text-black font-semibold">listening to</div>
              <MusicProfile />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="activity-card group default-bg sm:col-span-4 relative">
            <div class="absolute h-full w-full z-10 linear-fade-bg">
              <div class="lowercase !text-white font-semibold">reading</div>
            </div>
            <Image width="1600" height="1024" src="/books.webp" alt="Books Reading Now" loading="eager" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-any smooth" />
          </div>

          <div class="activity-card group default-bg sm:col-span-4 relative">
            <div class="absolute h-full w-full z-10 linear-fade-bg">
              <div class="lowercase !text-white font-semibold">envisioning</div>
            </div>
            <Image width="925" height="746" src="/vision.webp" alt="Vision board" loading="eager" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-any smooth" />
          </div>

          <div class="activity-card default-bg sm:col-span-3">
            <div class="p-4 flex flex-col h-full justify-between">
              <div class="lowercase font-semibold">learning</div>
              <ul class="font-light space-y-3 mb-2 text-lg">
                <li>French (DELF B2)</li>
                <li>HCI & A11Y</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-start-6 lg:col-span-4 space-y-5 opacity-85 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        <div class="opacity-100 text-2xl pb-4">...</div>
        <div>
          Again, I’m Feyisola (shortform ‘Sola’) and I design software products. I have had the privilege of working with great people on different projects from AI to marketplaces, fintech, health
          tech, back-office software and non-profits. Here’s a <span class="underline opacity-100">
            <a target="_blank" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1i6HI6u8eUSnKqpk5Go6FNOWhBe5TN7zJ/view">3-min video</a>
          </span> where I go over my background.
        </div>
        <div>Currently, I do cool stuff at Kuda.  However in the future, I would like to retire to a hilltop lined with trees, a clear view when watching the sunset - first I have to afford it.</div>
        <div>
          In my free time, you can find me reading fiction, exercising or watching <span><Icon name="youtube" class="text-red-600 inline-block w-6 h-6 pb-0.5" /></span> The Office YouTube channel. Fun
          fact, I <span class="underline opacity-100"><a target="_blank" href="https://x.com/solaszn/status/1531102663303217154?s=20">trained my left-handwriting</a></span> and sometimes I sketch stuff
          like furniture or buildings. (PS: I wanted to be an architect)
        </div>
        <div>Have something in common? <a class="underline opacity-100" href="/contact">Let’s talk</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .activity-card {
    @apply h-[180px] overflow-hidden;
  }
  .linear-fade-bg {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 20%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 40%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%);
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .default-bg {
    @apply bg-[#AEAEAE]/15;
  }
</style>
